name: marine-transportation-data-data-catalog-e2539
notes: The Marine Transportation data inventory contains an overview of available marine transportation related information that is either used or produced by the Federal Government. This inventory is made available to provide analysts, managers, and decision makers with data and information useful for statistical and performance measurement. This inventory is the product of the Committee on the Marine Transportation Data Collection and Information Management Integrated Action Team (IAT), led by the Maritime Administration.
